Supported image formats to start with: png, jpg/jpeg, bmp, webp

Start with just console app? GUI comes later

User can select the type of compression (lossy or lossless), and the type of method.
User can choose where to save the new file.




https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_compression#Lossy_and_lossless_image_compression as a starting point for general research

Project structure
parent/
  makefile(/) -> script(s) to build the project
  src/ -> project files
  include/ -> public header files (.h)
  bin/ -> executables (.exe files)
  lib/ -> third party libraries
  docs/ -> Documentation
  README.md

Additional?
  build/ -> intermediate build files (like .o files)
  tests/ -> unit tests
